## 🔄 Recent Updates (v2.0.0)
✅ **Improved UI**: **Automatic center alignment and dynamic spacing adjustments**  
✅ **New Time Zone Support**: **Seoul (KST) and Los Angeles (PST/PDT) now included**  
✅ **Multi-Language Support**: **10 languages available, with flag-based selection**  
✅ **Better Time Display**: **Consistently uses the 24-hour format**  

---

## 💻 System Requirements
- 🖥️ **OS**: Windows 7 / 8 / 10 / 11
- 📦 **.NET Framework**: 4.7.2 or later
- 💾 **Disk Space**: Less than 10MB

---

## 🛠️ How to Use
1️⃣ **Download and run `GameTimeConverter.exe`**  
2️⃣ **Select game time** (using **dropdown menus** for year, month, day, and time)  
3️⃣ **Time will be instantly converted and displayed**  
4️⃣ **Switch between 10 languages using flag-based selection**  

